            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">So for each book in the bookshelf, we (<strong>can do everything with it</strong>) print it. Pretty simple and intuitive. That’s Python.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
