        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">Remember that our vehicle <strong>class</strong> has four <strong>attributes</strong>: number of wheels, type of tank, seating capacity, and maximum velocity. We set all these <strong>attributes</strong> when creating a vehicle <strong>object</strong>. So here, we define our <strong>class</strong> to receive data when it initiates it:</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
