            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">This is an implementation of two methods: <strong>number_of_wheels</strong> and <strong>set_number_of_wheels</strong>. We call it <code>getter</code> & <code>setter</code>. Because the first gets the attribute value, and the second sets a new value for the attribute.</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
